item.title: export
item.description: cdsctl admin metadata workflow export export CDS Workflow Metadata Synopsis export CDS Workflow Metadata cdsctl admin metadata workflow export [flags] Options --export-file string Filename of file created (default "export_metadata_workflows.csv") Options inherited from parent commands -c, --context string cdsctl context name -f, --file string set configuration file --insecure (SSL) This option explicitly allows curl to perform "insecure" SSL connections and transfers. -n, --no-interactive Set to disable interaction with ctl --verbose Enable verbose output SEE ALSO cdsctl admin metadata workflow - Manage CDS Workflow Metadata
